Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有结果的恋爱有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的东西和从未拥有过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否一样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对……对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才……说的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和你听到的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 喜欢 很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候 什么时候的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说是分界线的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是可以说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……很不好意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有对阿久说……说……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可能不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说……说……说……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（打算什么时候说呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 好好说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惊讶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我完全没发觉这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来老师虽然是老了点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也算是个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是因为我没想过这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我完全是个局外人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把想的东西什么都说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我得去……阿久……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[得去告诉她]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要你去说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田小姐 给我安静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 西班牙那边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老……老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚听那边的丹下教授说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我感到好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我感觉好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的没关系吗 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样突然辞掉大学的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后的生活费怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会轮到你替我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直在帮徳大寺老师出书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以几个出版社有交工作给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以去当面向大众的美术研究班当讲师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很顽强的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你真的决定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你告诉我阿久的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很早就想联系你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是怕你会担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹豫了一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我找到了森田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样到底好不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会不会反而做了件多余的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森田的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经尽力让事情这样发展了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说我觉得只能这么发展下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都以为阿久是喜欢森田的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是 生存的意义和什么相关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人是为恋爱而活的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有些人不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 阿久被身体里那些必须去做的事情驱使着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是比恋爱更重要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是哪个重要哪个正确的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也是无法盘算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是在烦恼之前本能就先做出判断而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要离开这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于想要离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢您的照顾 丹下老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为喜欢这里才留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来却似找不到出口才留在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田出事后你一直不能正视自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你一半的生命都随他而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自从你把那女孩带来以后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那一半又渐渐回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹下老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到你拯救那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其实也是拯救你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实早就想飞回来看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果耽误了重要的工作那才糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 肯定还会骂人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是真山阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被他教训了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回去我们也帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会给老师增加负担
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这六年来以自己的方式和老师一起渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解的花本是一位令人尊敬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 说什么呢 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候才能不给我添麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说买断了我们公司的股份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么让你们怨恨的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍掉了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样院子里的树木就能安稳过冬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来还真是多亏了神的保佑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有人光以保持这院子的绿化为条件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就免费把这么大的房子租给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我没管好公司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们受这样的苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前大家分居各处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又能在同一个屋檐下生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这里的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 城山 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 你们……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道会这样 他们……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是城山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿馨少爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这么长时间都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边等着您盖章的文件在桌子上堆得像山一样多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和大家都一直在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有阿忍少爷说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事一定要告诉阿馨少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 阿馨少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您对从全世界的f1层那里每月半永久性获得190日圆的系统有没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,230日圆的话就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天中午到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集大家进行会议的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍少爷也会跑来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你们准备饭菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松田先生一定会干劲十足的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 城山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和小美很像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只白鸽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛圆圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿势很端正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口的毛软软地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有粉红色的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月医生说复健期间多接触粘土有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想学小美做试着做陶器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我想做一只白鸽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出来的第一只送给小美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后第二只送给新妈妈和小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道来不来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子明年春天才出生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在春天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫做“唷”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城山 也给阿忍来份咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加些肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城山 你哭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿馨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想去彼特的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说我都很喜欢那个老头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那家公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为呢 办公室一停电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就拿出光剑乱打一气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每个人都玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会那样胡来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了父亲我所知道的就只有他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的傻瓜公司也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟我说 她说会一直注视我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是一个很厉害的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就看穿了我想逃避一切的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是被她打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不要逃避大家一起奋斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避只能是一时的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来还真是过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说会一直注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能好好加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是想调整自己重新站在她的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些新的玩意给她看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉眼前终于亮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我似乎也有点明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸想说的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到了春天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和出院后的阿久从滨美毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为竹本和阿久的顺利毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时欢送竹本的盛冈之行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼特罗卡斯和森田一起的电视节目是……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是电影频道的特别节目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森田完全成了个职业电影人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一副很了不起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他没变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森田你终于下定决心了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 说我自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天坐几点的新干线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个 9点半
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经收拾好退房了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你今晚住哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去买几个冰激凌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对啊 冰激凌很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 竹本 你和她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就哭出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想能被竹本君修缮的寺院一定很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看着你做那座塔就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹本君不会偷工减料 草草了事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是会用心去修缮它们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想那些寺院一定会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会输给竹本君你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会治好右手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就没什么可以报答阿修的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师要的不是阿久的报答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是想找回他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 老师一定能找回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹本君 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面积6叠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（6张塌塌米大小）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无淋浴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到大学步行10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋龄28年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房租34000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的阳光很刺眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝东的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21号站台往盛冈方向的山彦49号列车马上要开车了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 这样很安静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹本君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久 你怎么……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹本君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些…… 全都是……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的幸福都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:19:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 一直都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有结果的恋爱有没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的东西和从未拥有过的东西是否一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喜欢上你 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着时光的流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都会成为回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起寻找着相同东西的那些不可思议的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将伴随着甜蜜的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远停留在我们的内心深处让我怀念
